</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Michael Cohen, Former Trump Lawyer, To Meet With House, Senate Committees</b>   <b data-is-speakable>The onetime attorney and fixer has closed meetings scheduled with the House and Senate intelligence panels and an open one set for the House oversight committee. It could be a doozy.</b>
