<!-- END ID="RES697816130" CLASS="BUCKETWRAP INTERNALLINK MEDIAPROMO PRIMARY" -->
   <p>Those "other matters" could include the <a href="https://www.npr.org/2019/01/17/686182230/trumps-ex-lawyer-cohen-acknowledges-scheme-to-rig-polls-in-presidential-race">online polls in 2014 and 2015 that Cohen admitted rigging</a> to help Trump's presidential aspirations, or the prospect of illicit foreign contributions to Trump's inauguration committee, or the access to Trump that <a href="https://www.npr.org/2018/05/11/610419846/at-t-admits-mistake-in-hiring-trump-lawyer-top-company-lobbyist-steps-down">Cohen sold to big corporate clients</a> in 2017.</p>   <p>Republicans have their own agenda.</p>   <p><strong>Lots to discuss with lawmakers</strong></p>   <p><a href="https://www.npr.org/2018/08/21/640544009/donald-trumps-longtime-attorney-michael-cohen-reaches-plea-deal-with-feds">Cohen has pleaded guilty to a number of crimes</a>, including arranging payments to two women ahead of Election Day in 2016 to buy their silence about alleged sexual relationships with Trump from years before.</p>   <div id="res697817398" class="bucketwrap internallink insettwocolumn inset2col ">
            <div class="bucket img">
                  <a id="featuredStackSquareImage640544009" href="https://www.npr.org/2018/08/21/640544009/donald-trumps-longtime-attorney-michael-cohen-reaches-plea-deal-with-feds"  data-metrics='{"category":"Story to Story","action":"Click Internal Link","label":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/2018\/08\/21\/640544009\/donald-trumps-longtime-attorney-michael-cohen-reaches-plea-deal-with-feds"}' ><img src="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2018/08/21/ap_18233518796405-edit_sq-ed0f8af8374b38ace68ec34d71796e798074f41f-s100-c15.jpg" data-original="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2018/08/21/ap_18233518796405-edit_sq-ed0f8af8374b38ace68ec34d71796e798074f41f-s100.jpg" class="img lazyOnLoad"  alt="Donald Trump's Attorney And Fixer Michael Cohen Pleads Guilty To 8 Federal Counts" /></a>         <div class="bucketblock">
                        <h3 class="slug"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/law/">Law </a></h3>
            <h3><a href="https://www.npr.org/2018/08/21/640544009/donald-trumps-longtime-attorney-michael-cohen-reaches-plea-deal-with-feds"  data-metrics='{"category":"Story to Story","action":"Click Internal Link","label":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/2018\/08\/21\/640544009\/donald-trumps-longtime-attorney-michael-cohen-reaches-plea-deal-with-feds"}' >Donald Trump's Attorney And Fixer Michael Cohen Pleads Guilty To 8 Federal Counts</a></h3>
         </div>
         
<!-- END CLASS="BUCKETBLOCK" -->
      </div>
      
